data.description: Happiness is eating tacos in your dream home. Buy this house, eat tacos, be happy... This is the one you are looking for!! 3 full bedrooms with a bonus room that could be a 4th bedroom(has a closet), 2 full baths spacious open concept and the covered patio of your dreams for those backyard BBQs! This house shows like new, and will not disappoint! The office space is currently setup as a man cave and has smart light features which can cycle through color choices but could easily be setup as an additional bedroom or a true office. The secondary bedrooms are wired and blocked for ceiling fans. This neighborhood will bring a true sense of community and create years of memories swimming in the community pool! Conveniently located near schools, shopping and an easy commute to DFW all move in ready for you to start making those amazing memories!!
